## Project Description
This project demonstrates a cloud-based car maintenance reminder system hosted on Amazon 
EC2 using Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS). The website allows users to view vehicle maintenance 
information and future service reminders through a web browser. The project was deployed on an Ubuntu 
Linux server using Nginx. A custom domain name was connected to the server and HTTPS security was enabled
using a free SSL/TLS certificate from Let's Encrypt.

The purpose of this project is to help users keep track of important vehicle tasks such as:
-Oil Changes
-Tire replacement
-Brake servicing
-General vehicle servicing

## Cloud Technologies Used
- Amazon EC2
- Ubuntu Linux
- Nginx Web Server
- DNS Configuration
- Let's Encrypt SSL/TLS
- SSH
